----------------------------------------------------------------------

    0031  Acknowledgement request

    Desc:

    Repr: n1

    1       if sender requests acknowledgement, i.e. UNB and UNZ segments received and identified

----------------------------------------------------------------------


    0035 Test indicator

    Desc:

    Repr: n1

    1       if the interchange is a test. Otherwise not used

----------------------------------------------------------------------

    0073   First and last transfer

    Desc:

    Repr: a1

    C      Creation, must be present for first transfer if more than one foreseen

    F      Final, must be present for last transfer

----------------------------------------------------------------------

    0081  Section identification

    Desc:   Separates sections in a message by one of the following codes

    Repr: a1

    D     separates the header and detail sections
    S     separates the detail and summary sections


